title: Just came back and queued for ranked...
body:
Just came back after quitting for like a month so I queue for ranked. I call mid as second pick but first pick takes it so I just go jungle. Then our fourth pick goes ADC after last pick called it then the last pick locks in ADC after we needed a top laner. Then his duo buddy (first pick who took mid) says "last pick called it" when ranked is pick order. Dumbass hypocrite stole mid after I called it then he's saying that about his duo.

Love the community.
